<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū wǒ men de xī wàng yé sū xiàn dài rén de xī wàng
 yé sū róng qù zhī tóu de hán shuāng yé sū gěi wǒ zhǐ chū fāng xiàng
 shēng mìng de huó shuǐ liú xiàng wàn guó wàn bāng
 lǜ shù chéng yīn dào lù huī huáng
 shēng mìng de huó shuǐ liú xiàng wàn guó wàn bāng,
 wǒ men yī lù gē chàng zǒu xiàng yuǎn fāng.</lyrics>
<title>yé sū gěi nǐ zhǐ chū fāng xiàng 迦南242</title>
<hymn_number>242</hymn_number>
